==English==
===Noun===
'''necklace''' (''plural'' '''necklaces''')

#An article of [[jewelry]]/[[jewellery]] that is worn around the [[neck]], most often made of a string of [[precious metal]], [[pearl]]s, [[gem]]s, [[bead]]s or [[shell]]s, and sometimes having a [[pendant]] attached.
#(''figurative'') Anything resembling a necklace in shape.
#:''a '''necklace''' of coral islands''
#A method of [[informal]] [[execution]] in which a [[rubber]] [[tyre]] is filled with [[petrol]], placed around the [[victim]]'s neck, and set on [[fire]].

